{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3454300/extras/ENGAdventure_.png?t=1740661033\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3454300/extras/Adventure.gif?t=1740661033\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Outrun the law, blast aliens, and fight for love in the wildest ride through the Wild West!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">West Escape throws you into a chaotic frontier where the law is on your tail and alien invaders are wreaking havoc. As a fugitive desperate to reunite with your lost love, you'll need to collect scrap, upgrade your gear, and face off against relentless extraterrestrial threats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3454300/extras/ENGDefend.png?t=1740661033\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3454300/extras/Defend.gif?t=1740661033\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast-paced combat keeps you on your toes\u2014dodge deadly attacks and strike back with revolvers, shotguns, and more. Every battle and upgrade brings you one step closer to freedom and the ultimate showdown in this explosive mix of Wild West grit and sci-fi action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3454300/extras/ENGCraft.png?t=1740661033\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3454300/extras/Craft.gif?t=1740661033\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High-Energy Combat: Dodge enemy attacks and blast aliens with powerful weapons like revolvers and shotguns.</p>